{"tid":122121,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[Steam][Survival] Infestation: The New Z 勝者為王 敗者為寇","createTime":"2017-02-15T19:41:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T04:39:51.000Z","uid":69193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de736bde306a5f58ee2136e57d638bce05146e25","tid":122121,"uid":69193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T19:41:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/555570/header.jpg  \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.akamai.steamstatic.com%2Fsteam%2Fapps%2F555570%2Fheader.jpg%E2%80%A8%E2%80%A8&h=b2d39ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n官網: <a href=\"http://playnewz.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fplaynewz.com%2F&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=5ba8d600\" target=\"_blank\">http://playnewz.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n Steam link: <a href=\"http://store.steampowered.com/app/555570/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F555570%2F&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=684f37b4\" target=\"_blank\">http://store.steampowered.com/app/555570/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">簡介: </span></strong><br />\n<br />\nInfestation: The New Z 係一隻一款殭屍生存大型多人開放世界遊戲，<span style=\"color: red;\">玩家同玩家之間嘅對戰係呢隻遊戲嘅重點，唔存在要周圍執食物去透爐BBQ嘅玩法</span>，因為好難餓死。<br />\n<br />\nWar Z 係呢隻遊戲嘅前身，經過唔同版本嘅演替出 Infestation: The New Z。前者飽受穿牆自描外掛困擾，後者<span style=\"color: red;\">防外掛系統比較完善</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">課金問題:</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n呢隻遊戲課金唔會令你勁啲，課金亦主要買 Premium account<br />\n<br />\nPremium account 主要有以下作用:<br />\n<br />\n1. 人物死左即刻復活唔洗比錢 or 等時間 （你亦可以等3分鐘 or 比 ＄15000 遊戲幤復活）<br />\n2. 每日送禮物（睇你運氣，通常垃圾）<br />\n3. 雙經雙錢<br />\n<br />\n由於經常都有雙倍點數嘅活動，課金亦都相當抵<br />\n呢加黎講 40 HKD ＝ 4個月 Premium account<br />\n<br />\n一齊玩嘅有人課金亦有人冇課金<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">特點:</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n1. Global Inventory<br />\n<br />\n係遊戲世界執完野（死會跌裝），可以登出伺服器，擺係大廳嘅Global Invetory （留返下次用）<br />\n<br />\n2. Skill Tree<br />\n<br />\n殺人 or 殺殭屍會攞到經驗值，經驗值可以用黎升級自己隻人物，例如冇咁易比殭屍察覺，瞄準器會再準啲之類。長玩嘅遲早都會升哂，但我地一班長玩嘅都未升哂，所以都算耐玩。<br />\n<br />\n3. Skin<br />\n<br />\nSkin 唔會有數值加成，係令呢隻遊戲耐玩度增加嘅其中一個因素。唔少 Skin 係會發哂光咁，一來型，二來招搖，變相會係地圖報自己位，對於有實力嘅人黎講，會無形中道出四字真言 : 夠做埋黎。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">開心玩 Gameplay</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w39xGgi_Yek\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dw39xGgi_Yek&d=%2Bo9ZPOFl8lx%2FL2stOySvpMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=ccdae6a8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w39xGgi_Yek</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有興趣一齊玩歡迎入黎RC <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nRC: 26397891 （活躍玩家暫時6-7人） <br />\n<br />\n有咩問題都可以入黎問</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"31f2b821837cef1c1366c035cfc6876d0f3ee03a","tid":122121,"uid":69193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T19:44:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: navy;\"><strong>新朋友注意事項:</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 盡量用近戰武器打殭屍，用槍會暴露自己位置<br />\n<br />\n2. 夜晚請帶夜視鏡<br />\n<br />\n3. 最好聯群結黨（2-3人）去執物資，安全啲<br />\n<br />\n4. 所有食物可以唔洗刻意執，肚餓只會扣血，唔會死<br />\n<br />\n5. 主要執步槍，e.g. M4A1, SIG556, L85, HONEY BADGER<br />\n<br />\n6. 唔等洗嘅步槍可以拆左排彈匣出黎，大部分彈匣都通用於其他步槍<br />\n<br />\n7. 敵人未發現你可以試下行近啲先殺，易爆頭，一兩粒足以收頭<br />\n<br />\n8. 善用藥物，盡量保持滿血，以免被收皮，建議藥物放快捷鍵<br />\n<br />\n9. 善用盾 (Riot Shield/Wood Shield) 擋子彈，保護自己，建議盾放快捷鍵<br />\n<br />\n10. 避免用錢復活角色同係商城買野，錢可儲起同其他玩家交易商城嘅野(平啲) or Skin<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">新手過來人有感:</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n開始果陣比人虐待真係幾慘 <br />\n雖然我呢加都係，但情況有好轉 <br />\n<br />\n呢隻遊戲嘅真理就係要埋堆 <br />\n三五成群出去冧友搶裝 <br />\n唔小心奉獻左性命 <br />\n就轉個頭返入去覆灼 <br />\n<br />\n如果覺得玩到冇目標 <br />\n短期黎講緊係要儲齊彈藥 <br />\n同人開片至少都準備好頭盔呀，盔甲呀，槍啦大佬 <br />\n長遠黎講我想虐待返其他人 <br />\n<br />\n唔好灰心！堅持！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">Q&amp;A</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nQ: 唔課金玩得唔得<br />\nA: 得。<br />\n<br />\nQ: 車點用？<br />\nA: 車只可以係 Beginner Server / Premium Server / Private Server 用，對住部車按實 F5 可以收返部車。<br />\n<br />\nQ: 我得一個人，可以點玩？<br />\nA: 可以簡啲最少人嘅 Server，因為呢啲 Server 都係單人出團勝地，你得一個時人地都係得一個，自己安全執下野咁。<br />\n<br />\nQ: Beginner Server 可以玩幾耐？<br />\nA: 72 Hours<br />\n<br />\nQ: 點入 Official Server？<br />\nA: 係 Beginner Server 生存 1 Hour"},{"pid":"a293faf7293b8ef30cb35af8ca9a04a1366305a4","tid":122121,"uid":69193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T02:26:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1d5eae36d72977c4077a7e8ac9a5456601e99ca","tid":122121,"uid":39087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T07:04:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85c516ece5a54c8be854ba66d8d4734cef88dd7f","tid":122121,"uid":69193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T08:39:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7621e5741799b65fc79ef32278cb14492233812","tid":122121,"uid":69193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T09:40:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bd1763bdda694e78bf967208da8c4c0b02b6581","tid":122121,"uid":69193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T12:46:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbc5bcc4d510bfa4a0a02e04020defe874201cc5","tid":122121,"uid":5770,"like":0,"dislik